item.title: Need help making website [html]
item.dc:creator: @_Kane † Kane †
item.description:
@_Kane wrote:

Download a free trial of Dreamweaver. It’s an HTML editor from Adobe and it’s really self-explanatory. You can look some guides up online, but basically it lets you make a website without coding anything.

http://www.adobe.com/cfusion/tdrc/index.cfm?product=dreamweaver&loc=en_us

Unless you wanna spend money on something you’ll probably never use again.
